{"tid":2288140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指藏鎅刀螺絲批 女設計師獲判無罪 官：逃跑可有清白原因 工具可有合法用途","createTime":"2020-11-16T09:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T09:38:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9c1ce65d8571559807ac95c7c06a905d8ddfb1","tid":2288140,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"女櫥窗設計師被指去年11 月，在旺角與一名男子糾纏，她其後逃走，遭警員截查及搜出鎅刀及螺絲批等物品。設計師否認一項管有攻擊性武器罪受審，今（16 日）在西九龍裁判法院獲裁定罪名不成立。裁判官劉淑嫻指，雖然當時穿黑衫的被告行為可疑，但涉案物品並非特製或改裝，其同事亦供稱物品會在工作時使用，故不排除有合法用途。裁判官又指，被告早在警員大叫「咪走」之前已逃跑，不排除逃跑有清白原因。法庭宣判結果後，公眾席有人拍掌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E9%8E%85%E5%88%80%E8%9E%BA%E7%B5%B2%E6%89%B9-%E5%A5%B3%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A4%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98-%E9%80%83%E8%B7%91%E5%8F%AF%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%85%E7%99%BD%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%8F%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%258E%2585%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%259E%25BA%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2580%2583%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2580%2594%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1a2fc48b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%258E%2585%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%259E%25BA%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2580%2583%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%25